---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Blog from '../../../layouts/blog.astro';
import '../../../assets/files/journal.css';

export const frontmatter = {
  title: "Dead pixels",
  date: "260604",
};
---

<Layout title={frontmatter.date + " " + frontmatter.title} url="https://Loveisdancing.com/files/blog/260604">

    <Blog
    
    date={frontmatter.date}
    title={frontmatter.title}
    caption="Photos by Ben Burton."
    backgroundColor="black"
    textColor="white"
    invertLogo={true}

    >
    
<!--     <div slot="image" class="blogimg"></div> -->
<!--     <img src="/content/images/dead-pixels/snarl.jpg" slot="image" class="blogimg"> -->

    <div slot="image" class="carousel">
        <div class="track">
            <div class="group">
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
            </div>
            <div aria-hidden class="group">
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max1_edit.jpg"></div>
                <div class="card"><img src="/content/images/blog/260604/max2_edit.jpg"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p slot="journal">
        I want to write. 
    </p>
        
    <p slot="journal">
        Last night I took photos with Ben Burton and it was so fun. Halfway through I started coughing like crazy and that definitely brought down my focus, but we made it! I'm so grateful to have the opportunity to work with cool people like Ben. He said something that I think will stick with me for a long time... something along the lines of "I like to work with musicians because they have such big ideas." At that moment, I was like, "He gets it." I think not having a super clear direction for the photos worked out in our favor because we spent time experimenting. Which is something I love doing.
    </p>

    <p slot="journal">
        I started adding dead pixels to images on this site through a custom TouchDesigner patch because I thought it would look cool.
    </p>

    <p slot="journal">
        #peace
    </p>

    <audio slot="audio" autoplay loop id="bgaudio">
    <source src="/content/audio/fx/dance_chords.ogg" type="audio/mpeg">
    </audio>

    </Blog>

    <script>
    var audio = document.getElementById("bgaudio") as HTMLAudioElement;
    audio.volume = 0.2;
    </script>

</Layout>